'''哈德姆·穆罕默德帕夏'''（{{lang-tr|Hadım Mehmet Paşa}}），是一名出身[[格魯吉亞人|格魯吉亞人]]的[[鄂圖曼帝國|鄂圖曼帝國]]政治家<ref name="Erkan32">İsmail Hâmi Danişmend, ''Osmanlı Devlet Erkânı'', Türkiye Yayınevi, İstanbul, 1971, p. 32.</ref>。

他在1622年9月21日至1623年2月5日出任[[大维齐尔|大维齐尔]]<ref name="Erkan32"/>，也曾於1604-05年間出任[[埃及省|埃及省]]的總督<ref name="sicilli">{{citation|author=Mehmet Süreyya|editor1=Nuri Akbayar|editor2=Seyit A. Kahraman|title=Sicill-i Osmanî|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=btElAQAAMAAJ|year=1996|publisher=Türkiye Kültür Bakanlığı and Türkiye Ekonomik ve Toplumsal Tarih Vakfı|location=Beşiktaş, Istanbul|language=tr|origyear=1890|isbn=9789753330411|accessdate=2018-06-13|archive-date=2021-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210104055811/https://books.google.com/books?id=btElAQAAMAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Holt2009-Beylicate">{{cite journal|last1=Holt|first1=P. M.|title=The beylicate in Ottoman Egypt during the seventeenth century|journal=Bulletin of the School of Oriental and African Studies|volume=24|issue=2|year=2009|pages=227–229|issn=0041-977X|doi=10.1017/S0041977X00091424}}</ref><ref name="CookAhmed2011">{{cite book|author1=Michael A. Cook|author2=Asad Ahmed|author3=Behnam Sadeghi|author4=Michael Bonner|title=The Islamic Scholarly Tradition: Studies in History, Law, and Thought in Honor of Professor Michael Allan Cook|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=riMyFm6hOjkC&pg=PA154|date=21 March 2011|publisher=BRILL|isbn=978-90-04-19435-9|pages=154|access-date=2018-06-13|archive-date=2020-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200627192534/https://books.google.com/books?id=riMyFm6hOjkC&pg=PA154|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

